{"tid":1253203,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"【婚訊】聲優竹達彩奈與梶裕貴結婚","createTime":"2019-06-23T12:23:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-23T13:49:51.000Z","uid":75050,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2cde2d0380104ce1387cf6d5a4e8a64a833711a9","tid":1253203,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T12:23:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://greatgame.asia/【婚訊】聲優竹達彩奈與梶裕貴結婚/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgreatgame.asia%2F%E3%80%90%E5%A9%9A%E8%A8%8A%E3%80%91%E8%81%B2%E5%84%AA%E7%AB%B9%E9%81%94%E5%BD%A9%E5%A5%88%E8%88%87%E6%A2%B6%E8%A3%95%E8%B2%B4%E7%B5%90%E5%A9%9A%2F&d=Y7KpFbDUA2jerjE4fgLr1xzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=1e71bc42\" target=\"_blank\">https://greatgame.asia/【婚訊】聲優竹達彩奈與梶裕貴結婚/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GVA2oHE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGVA2oHE.jpg&h=27be3a6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【婚訊】聲優竹達彩奈與梶裕貴結婚<br />\n<br />\n超人氣聲優竹達彩奈(30)與梶裕貴(33)於6月23日在twitter上宣佈結婚，成為令和第一對成婚的人氣聲優夫妻，一眾聲優和動畫監督等業界人士都在twitter留言祝賀。兩人各自在twitter上以手寫文的方式，發表了這次婚訊，過去他們都曾經在動畫《銀河美少年》、《罪惡王冠》、《惡魔高校》等作品合作過。<br />\n<br />\n今年6月23日同時是竹達彩奈的30歲生日，兩年前28歲的竹達彩奈擔任綜藝節目《超人氣法律諮詢事務所》（行列のできる法律相談所）的嘉賓時，曾經提過事務所禁止她雖然不是偶像，但在30歲前禁止談戀愛專心事業，結果在30歲當天馬上宣佈婚訊，是不是已經等待這一天很久了呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JjrUePy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJjrUePy.jpg&h=c5874f3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DhCkanU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDhCkanU.jpg&h=da1179a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n竹達彩奈twitter原文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Ayana_take/status/1142600080433696768\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAyana_take%2Fstatus%2F1142600080433696768&d=Y7KpFbDUA2jerjE4fgLr1xzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=a139ba46\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAyana_take%2Fstatus%2F1142600080433696768&h=f863e5d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Ayana_take/status/1142600080433696768</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UheuN9H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUheuN9H.jpg&h=65fb6570&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n梶裕貴twitter原文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/KAJI_staff/status/1142598267957587968\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FKAJI_staff%2Fstatus%2F1142598267957587968&d=Y7KpFbDUA2jerjE4fgLr1xzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=fd31b782\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FKAJI_staff%2Fstatus%2F1142598267957587968&h=ec4cbd89\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/KAJI_staff/status/1142598267957587968</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BnEbg3b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBnEbg3b.jpg&h=174dfaab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"616f10be680fd1cfc10e8a25a7b061e952ecb12c","tid":1253203,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T12:25:05.000Z","msg":"五等分作者 春場祝賀竹達彩奈結婚<br />\ntwitter @negi_haruba<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bRAhW4B.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbRAhW4B.png&h=2e3a30e5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eaf3b196f300bc7f9f6e159c4d37c2658b930959","tid":1253203,"uid":75050,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T13:49:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}